title: Lincoln Chafee drops out of presidential race ‘after much thought’
text:
Lincoln Chafee drops out of presidential race ‘after much thought’ 
Published By: Boston.com - Today 
Longshot Democratic presidential candidate Lincoln Chafee bowed out of the 2016 race on Friday, he said in a statement....
